@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.06
    v2 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.97 * v2 + 0.42) + wp.abs(v0 + 0.49)))
    v0 = wp.sin((wp.abs(tmp + 0.61) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.93)))
    v0 = (v0 / (wp.cos(v1 + 0.20) - wp.sin(v0 + 0.20)))
    tmp = 0.39
    v0 = v1
    tmp = 0.91
    data[tid] = v0
